"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"1月13日消息，加密交易平台BitMEX聘请前Coinbase Global Inc. 执行官 Marcus Hughes 担任 BitMEX 首席风险官，并向BitMEX首席执行官 Alexander Hoptner 汇报。 Marcus Hughes 将领导与监管机构和政策制定者的合作，并在 BitMEX 扩展到新市场时建立其风险框架和合规计划。\",\"timestamp\":1642070149,\"title\":\"BitMEX聘请前Coinbase高管担任其首席风险官\"},\"digest\":\"RkvMKWL1pF2r358KfuqNkHuGwlfM2pumCNzvTBWDP3o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x1A8025F1DB45f9b943946Ad47b8A8eFeEbD2EeAA\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"4mnFiHyK4LuO7GD435xXgzRsPVfvFBZNtUksuuhcCQQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"pd8FrrXbKC_kHa2qcx5Op0A6qGwsJv_qQxhbmghc4zg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"vlxW_7x-YXsIMDX4GHX6z7C-SfshrSrXWYftWCx4nqtQ_hL3LJfl-IL-0Z2f58VUuADFh01ytn-CQFXNnhW7Vg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd4fc93aecb7c08a97ce0c79c147ba2527f9106227bb3f4ff6dacf015a27912727ba719aa570bebb4f8d557505c3963fcb2e75993c737a531590f75ed342982f31b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"4mnFiHyK4LuO7GD435xXgzRsPVfvFBZNtUksuuhcCQQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"pd8FrrXbKC_kHa2qcx5Op0A6qGwsJv_qQxhbmghc4zg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"RkvMKWL1pF2r358KfuqNkHuGwlfM2pumCNzvTBWDP3o\"}"